      "passage_index": 12,
      "title": "The Blackout All-Stars",
      "score": 0.12371848133525327,
      "text": "The Blackout All-Stars\nThe Blackout All-Stars was a one-off 1994 Latin supergroup consisting of Ray Barretto, Sheila E., Tito Puente, Tito Nieves, Paquito D'Rivera, Dave Valentin, Grover Washington, Jr., and Tony Pabon.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.05115437661290522,
